DOVE v1.7 (Release date: 2021-08-02)
==============

Changes:

* Changes to documentation regarding categorical covariates in model for dove()
* Incorporation of dove2() method and its updates to documentation
* Modifications to kernel smoothing method for dove() to impose constraint
  VE_a(0) = 0 and HR(0) = 1
* Changed example dataset and updated documentation to reflect this change

DOVE v1.6 (Release date: 2021-06-02)
==============

Changes:

* Allowed for categorical covariates in model
* Fixed bug when only 1 covariate provided in model

DOVE v1.5 (Release date: 2021-03-05)
==============

Changes:

* Added undoing of option changes made in dove and vignette

DOVE v1.4 (Release date: 2021-03-03)
==============

Changes:

* Changed bw to bandwidth
* Modified documentation

DOVE v1.3 (Release date: 2021-03-02)
==============

Changes:

* Add interval feature
* Changed to allow specification of smoother bandwidth

DOVE v1.2 (Release date: 2021-02-06)
==============

Changes:

* Modified documentation

DOVE v1.1 (Release date: 2021-02-04)
==============

Changes:

* Changed example dataset
* Changed smoothing of relative risk

